		TNT1 A 0 A_ChangeFlag("NOPAIN",0)
		LOWR O 10 A_FaceTarget
		LOWR PO 4 BRIGHT A_CPosAttack
		LOWR O 1 A_CPosRefire
		Goto Missile+2
